### **4. 32_StreamChartTunnel**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes fast-moving numeric streams using a smooth, scrollable real-time charting interface.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamChartTunnel - Realtime Scrolling Chart Renderer

StreamChartTunnel delivers real-time visual feedback for data streams in a timeline format, ideal for system metrics.

## Features
- Realtime line chart  
- Scrollable timeline  
- Adjustable refresh interval  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_StreamChartTunnel.git
cd 32_StreamChartTunnel
python visualize.py
